self_check_questions.answer:
```java
int dayTotal = 0;
for (int p = 0; p < sales.length; p++) {
    dayTotal += sales[p][3];
}
```
The column index is fixed at 3 (day 3), the row index iterates through all products. We're summing DOWN a column. The single loop is enough because only one index varies.

